    "description": "A young veterinarian, Sara, inherited the Animal Rescue Center from her uncle, who she thought did not love her at all.<br>When she came to the town to take over the Rescue Center, she realized that it was barely a Center at all – only an old house.<br><br>Nasty joke. Proof of how much her uncle didn’t like her.<br>Still… Inheritance is inheritance, and family is family after all… Sara accepts the challenge and enters a great adventure, deciding that she will renovate and decorate the building into a brand new Animal Rescue Center.<br><br>With the help of her new friends… and through numerous marble matching levels in this marble matching world, her plan may come to fruition.  Help Sara build a center where every animal can feel safe and free!<br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br><br>🌎 <strong>Many different, pleasantly crafted Locations</strong> - over 14 adventurous locations for enjoyable gameplay. :)<br>🌠 <strong>Over 120 interesting and challenging levels to test your skills in marble shooter extravaganza</strong> <br>🏡 <strong>Build and decorate</strong> - Collect stars through beating marble shooter levels and design your Animal Rescue shelter. <br>🥇 <strong>Get engaged in events and unlock achievements!</strong><br>🏃‍♀️💨 <strong>Fast and Easy gameplay</strong> - only use your mouse! Point, click, shoot!",
